    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Polendina Clan, Level 8+</p><p>Your construct nature has forced you to develop many kinds of skills on your own, as you were not blessed with the innate adaptability of normal human shinobi. This feat demonstrates your tenacity and mastery of your synthetic prowess. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>Increase your Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>Twice per long rest, when you would roll for initiative, you may immediately replenish your Synthetic Aura.</li><li>When you use your Action or Bonus Action to replenish your Synthetic Aura, you gain twice as many temporary hit points and half as many temporary chakra points.</li><li>When a weapon is in your Floating Array, its weapon damage die is increased by 1 step, up to a d10.</li><li>Increase your flight speed by +15 ft. Once per short rest, when you begin using your flight speed on your turn, you may gain the benefits of the Disengage action.</li></ul>",
